not be able to retrieve this
Swap Request again

Manage My Account
The administrator can select
“Manage My Account” to view Swap
Request history including:
•Date shipped
•Tracking no. details
•Proof of swap verification status

FAQ
Review FAQs to assist you with
any specific questions about the
Program.
If you need any more specific
details about your account or
device, you will need to go to the
Samsung B2B Knox Portal
If you can’t find the answer are
looking for in the FAQs, submit
an inquiry using the INQUIRY
FORM and our team will get
back to you in 1-2 business
days

Update IMEI
1
2
3
Click “UPDATE IMEI”, if your
enrolled IMEI no longer
matches as result of an in-
warranty swap
1
2Enter the IMEI of the new
device. **Tip To find the IMEI
of your device, type “*#06#”
on your phone.
3UPLOAD the proof of swap
document which shows the
details of the original IMEI
(registered with us) and the
new IMEI
**Important: If your registered device(s) have been swapped outside of the Samsung Care+ Program you
will need to provide us with the new IMEI details before your Swap Request can be processed.
For e.g., your device registered device(s) may have been swapped due to an in-warranty claim through
Samsung or your carrier
